{
  "stem": "3380.4",
  "chunk_idx": 8,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "He gave me orders to go, so I have to go.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So I went with a bunch of people.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "We went to a-- a place.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "They shipped us to a place by the Elbe not far from Magdeburg.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "They used to call it Schonebeck.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Like Schonebeck, you got [INAUDIBLE] here, Schonebeck by Magdeburg.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And I came in in that camp.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And then [? came-- ?] from the city came for the health department, and they start asking-- you know, they didn't even know what kind of people that came, or they need any kind of medication, or they tried to help us.",
      "word_count": 42
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And it's lucky me, the SS man came out and he said to him, what are you talking with that Jew over there?",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I mean, what kind of business have you got?",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "He said, I'm from the health department.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I just want to find out [? that ?] he needs any medication.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And he said, the Lagerfuhrer, he said, the SS man, we got anything what we need.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "We got our own.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "We got more than we need.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "So he had to leave.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And I became over there the doctor, and I was there.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We worked in a factory.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "People worked in a factory, and I was at home.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And I was-- I was the-- the-- the-- the head doctor of over the camp.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "That was more no more.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "We didn't have any medication.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "We didn't-- and lots of people died.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "It didn't matter it was a doctor or was a, you know, was a phony doctor.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "In any event, we were there until the Americans took over Magdeburg, and then an order came that we have to leave.",
      "word_count": 22
    }
  ],
